    // FAQ Content Section
    section.faq-content
      .container
        // Shipping Process FAQs
        .faq-category.active(data-category="shipping")
          .category-title
            h2 Shipping Process
          .faq-list
            .faq-item
              .faq-question
                h3 What temperature ranges do you support?
                .faq-toggle
                  svg(width="20", height="20", viewBox="0 0 20 20", fill="none")
                    path(d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5", stroke="currentColor", stroke-width="2", stroke-linecap="round", stroke-linejoin="round")
              .faq-answer
                p We support three main temperature ranges: Refrigerated (2-8°C) for standard pharmaceuticals and vaccines, Frozen (-20°C) for specialty products requiring deep freeze, and Ultra-Low (-80°C) for advanced therapies like cell and gene therapy products.
            
            .faq-item
              .faq-question
                h3 How do you ensure temperature stability during transit?
                .faq-toggle
                  svg(width="20", height="20", viewBox="0 0 20 20", fill="none")
                    path(d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5", stroke="currentColor", stroke-width="2", stroke-linecap="round", stroke-linejoin="round")
              .faq-answer
                p We use validated packaging systems with real-time temperature monitoring, insulated containers, and appropriate cooling agents (dry ice, liquid nitrogen vapor, or gel packs) depending on the temperature requirements. Our packaging is validated for specific time periods and transport conditions.
            
            .faq-item
              .faq-question
                h3 What documentation is provided with shipments?
                .faq-toggle
                  svg(width="20", height="20", viewBox="0 0 20 20", fill="none")
                    path(d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5", stroke="currentColor", stroke-width="2", stroke-linecap="round", stroke-linejoin="round")
              .faq-answer
                p Each shipment includes comprehensive documentation: temperature monitoring reports, chain of custody documentation, regulatory compliance certificates, customs documentation, and delivery confirmation. All documentation is available digitally through our tracking portal.

        // Tracking & Monitoring FAQs
        .faq-category(data-category="tracking")
          .category-title
            h2 Tracking & Monitoring
          .faq-list
            .faq-item
              .faq-question
                h3 How can I track my shipment?
                .faq-toggle
                  svg(width="20", height="20", viewBox="0 0 20 20", fill="none")
                    path(d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5", stroke="currentColor", stroke-width="2", stroke-linecap="round", stroke-linejoin="round")
              .faq-answer
                p You can track your shipment using our "Track Shipment" button in the top navigation, or by entering your tracking number on our tracking portal. We provide real-time updates on location, temperature conditions, and estimated delivery times.
            
            .faq-item
              .faq-question
                h3 What happens if there's a temperature excursion?
                .faq-toggle
                  svg(width="20", height="20", viewBox="0 0 20 20", fill="none")
                    path(d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5", stroke="currentColor", stroke-width="2", stroke-linecap="round", stroke-linejoin="round")
              .faq-answer
                p We have 24/7 monitoring systems that immediately alert our operations team and the client if any temperature excursion occurs. Our team will assess the situation, implement corrective actions, and provide detailed reports. We work closely with clients to determine the best course of action for affected products.
            
            .faq-item
              .faq-question
                h3 How often are temperature readings recorded?
                .faq-toggle
                  svg(width="20", height="20", viewBox="0 0 20 20", fill="none")
                    path(d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5", stroke="currentColor", stroke-width="2", stroke-linecap="round", stroke-linejoin="round")
              .faq-answer
                p Temperature readings are recorded every 15 minutes during transit, with immediate alerts for any excursions. For ultra-sensitive products, we can provide more frequent monitoring intervals as required.

        // Packaging & Storage FAQs
        .faq-category(data-category="packaging")
          .category-title
            h2 Packaging & Storage
          .faq-list
            .faq-item
              .faq-question
                h3 What packaging materials do you use?
                .faq-toggle
                  svg(width="20", height="20", viewBox="0 0 20 20", fill="none")
                    path(d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5", stroke="currentColor", stroke-width="2", stroke-linecap="round", stroke-linejoin="round")
              .faq-answer
                p We use a range of validated packaging systems including insulated containers, dry ice systems, liquid nitrogen vapor systems, and gel pack solutions. All packaging is validated for specific temperature ranges and transit times according to regulatory requirements.
            
            .faq-item
              .faq-question
                h3 How long can products maintain temperature stability?
                .faq-toggle
                  svg(width="20", height="20", viewBox="0 0 20 20", fill="none")
                    path(d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5", stroke="currentColor", stroke-width="2", stroke-linecap="round", stroke-linejoin="round")
              .faq-answer
                p Our packaging systems are validated for different time periods: Refrigerated (2-8°C) maintains stability for 72+ hours, Frozen (-20°C) for 96+ hours, and Ultra-Low (-80°C) for 120+ hours. Actual duration depends on ambient conditions and specific product requirements.
            
            .faq-item
              .faq-question
                h3 Do you provide packaging for small shipments?
                .faq-toggle
                  svg(width="20", height="20", viewBox="0 0 20 20", fill="none")
                    path(d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5", stroke="currentColor", stroke-width="2", stroke-linecap="round", stroke-linejoin="round")
              .faq-answer
                p Yes, we provide specialized packaging solutions for small shipments, including individual sample vials, clinical trial materials, and small batch quantities. Our packaging is scalable to accommodate various shipment sizes while maintaining temperature integrity.

        // Delivery & Customs FAQs
        .faq-category(data-category="delivery")
          .category-title
            h2 Delivery & Customs
          .faq-list
            .faq-item
              .faq-question
                h3 Do you handle customs clearance?
                .faq-toggle
                  svg(width="20", height="20", viewBox="0 0 20 20", fill="none")
                    path(d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5", stroke="currentColor", stroke-width="2", stroke-linecap="round", stroke-linejoin="round")
              .faq-answer
                p Yes, we provide comprehensive customs clearance services for international shipments. Our team handles all necessary documentation, regulatory compliance, and works with local customs authorities to ensure smooth clearance while maintaining cold chain integrity.
            
            .faq-item
              .faq-question
                h3 What are your delivery timeframes?
                .faq-toggle
                  svg(width="20", height="20", viewBox="0 0 20 20", fill="none")
                    path(d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5", stroke="currentColor", stroke-width="2", stroke-linecap="round", stroke-linejoin="round")
              .faq-answer
                p Delivery timeframes vary by destination and service level: Domestic deliveries typically take 1-3 days, international express 2-5 days, and standard international 5-10 days. For ultra-urgent shipments like cell and gene therapy products, we offer same-day and next-day delivery options.
            
            .faq-item
              .faq-question
                h3 Do you provide white-glove delivery services?
                .faq-toggle
                  svg(width="20", height="20", viewBox="0 0 20 20", fill="none")
                    path(d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5", stroke="currentColor", stroke-width="2", stroke-linecap="round", stroke-linejoin="round")
              .faq-answer
                p Yes, we offer white-glove delivery services for high-value and sensitive shipments. This includes direct delivery to specific locations, temperature-controlled handoff procedures, and specialized handling requirements as needed.

        // General Questions FAQs
        .faq-category(data-category="general")
