                h3 How do I get a quote for my shipment?
                .faq-toggle
                  svg(width="20", height="20", viewBox="0 0 20 20", fill="none")
                    path(d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5", stroke="currentColor", stroke-width="2", stroke-linecap="round", stroke-linejoin="round")
              .faq-answer
                p You can request a quote by clicking the "Get Quote" button in our navigation, filling out our contact form, or calling our customer service team. We'll need details about your shipment including origin, destination, temperature requirements, and product specifications.
            
            .faq-item
              .faq-question
                h3 Do you offer 24/7 customer support?
                .faq-toggle
                  svg(width="20", height="20", viewBox="0 0 20 20", fill="none")
                    path(d="M5 7.5L10 12.5L15 7.5", stroke="currentColor", stroke-width="2", stroke-linecap="round", stroke-linejoin="round")
              .faq-answer
                p Yes, we provide 24/7 customer support for all shipments. Our emergency support line is available for urgent issues, and our operations team monitors all active shipments around the clock to ensure timely intervention if needed.

